author: Pete Kasperowicz
title: Trump: Clinton's Russia 'reset' made the US look like a 'bunch of jerks'
text:
President Trump said Hillary Clinton 's famous "Russian reset" in 2009 made the U.S. look stupid, and said he would have been ridiculed if he tried something like that.
" Hillary Clinton did a reset, remember, with the stupid plastic button that made us all look like a bunch of jerks?" Trump said in a lengthy press conference at the White House. "[Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov] looked at her like, 'what the hell is she doing with that cheap plastic button?'"
" Hillary Clinton , that was a reset, remember it said 'reset?'" he said. "Now if I do that, ooh, I'm a bad guy."
